Subject: [PATCH 284/443] arm64: dts: renesas: update threshold temperature of
 system shutdown

Base on HW Manual of RZ/G Series, 2nd Generation, maximum temperature
of normal opreration is 110 degree Celcius.
Therefore, this commit will update this threshold temperature for all
RZ/G2 SoCs.

Signed-off-by: Hien Huynh <hien.huynh.px@renesas.com>
